    "attributes": {
      "name": "Beat Maker Studio Card",
      "summary": "A comprehensive card component for creating, managing, and sequencing drum patterns within a music production environment. It features an interactive 16-step sequencer grid, pattern library, and instrument kit selection, allowing users to compose rhythms by toggling beats and controlling instrument volumes. It supports real-time playback with adjustable BPM, swing, and master volume, and provides tools for pattern randomization, clearing, and loading presets. The card also includes a visually rich, responsive UI with multiple formats for different display sizes, facilitating both casual editing and detailed production.",
